---
import AppLayout from '../layouts/AppLayout.astro';

const title = 'Footy Analytics · Tools & Notes';
const jsonLd = {
  "@context":"https://schema.org",
  "@type":"WebSite",
  "name":"Footy Analytics",
  "url": Astro.request.url
};
---
<AppLayout title={title} description="轻量、可复用的足球模型工具：Poisson、Implied Odds、Kelly" jsonLd={jsonLd} active="home">
  <style>
    :root{--w:880px}
    h1{font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:.5rem}
    .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:1rem;margin-top:1rem}
    .card{border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:12px;padding:1rem;text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
    .card:hover{box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.06)}
    small{color:#666}
    header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem}
  </style>

  <header>
    <img alt="logo" src="/og-default.svg" width="28" height="28" />
    <strong>Footy Analytics</strong>
  </header>

  <h1>工具导航</h1>
  <p>Poisson → Fair Odds → Kelly，一个思路跑通三页工具。</p>

  <div class="grid">
    <a class="card" href="/tools/match-insights/">
      <h3>Match Insights ↗</h3>
      <p>λ 输入 → 比分矩阵 → 1X2 概率/公平赔率 → Kelly 建议。</p>
      <small>闭环演示页</small>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="/tools/implied-odds/">
      <h3>Implied Odds ↗</h3>
      <p>从任意 N 项市场赔率，计算隐含概率、归一化与公平赔率。</p>
      <small>适配十进制/美式/分数盘</small>
    </a>
    <a class="card" href="/tools/kelly/">
      <h3>Kelly ↗</h3>
      <p>给定 p 与赔率，批量算 Kelly 比例与下注额（含单注上限）。</p>
      <small>支持 bankroll 与 cap</small>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2 style="margin-top:2rem">说明</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>所有计算在浏览器本地完成，零第三方依赖。</li>
    <li>工具仅用于学习演示，不构成任何投注建议。</li>
  </ul>
</AppLayout>

  <div style="height:1rem"></div>
  <a class="card" href="/articles/">
    <h3>Articles ↗</h3>
    <p>模型笔记与使用示例。</p>
    <small>站内文档</small>
  </a>
